School Performance Analytics Dashboard | Power BI
Overview

This project demonstrates an end-to-end Business Intelligence workflow using Power BI. Starting from a single flat dataset containing student, teacher, school, academic performance, attendance, and financial information, the data was cleaned, transformed, modeled into a relational schema, and analyzed using DAX. The final solution is presented through an interactive Power BI report that supports data-driven decision making for school administrators.

Project Objectives
Clean and standardize inconsistent data using Power Query.
Normalize a flat dataset into a dimensional data model.
Build a star schema with appropriate fact and dimension tables.
Create reusable DAX measures for business analysis.
Develop an interactive Power BI report with filters and drill-down capabilities.
Generate insights into student performance, teacher allocation, school operations, and outstanding fee balances.
Tools & Technologies
